input png indexed images palette 15 colors


to convert image use imagemagick :

$ convert truecolor_source_image.png -colors 15 indexed_neogeo_image.png
Crop the image (converted image size should be : 256x256)
You may also use Gimp (png indexed image mode with 15 size palette)
Dithering algorithms ...
Option B : pixel art, produce png indexed image using 16 colors, 1 of the colors is transparent
...
